			description: [
				"This chapter will focus on advancing in &9Create: The Factory Must Grow&r and in logistics technologies."
				""
				"&e-&r Oil will be your focus in advancing as it is a great source of energy."
				"&e-&r Steel will also be very important in the rest of the entire modpack, it is the most used resource to make resistant components."
