		{
			dependencies: ["104E7094B28E8114"]
			description: [
				"Spirit altar is a ritual that infuses spirits and items, you can see its recipes in the &9JEI/EMI&r."
				""
				"The altar requires pillars to add other items, if you look at the JEI/EMI there is an item in the middle and others on the outside, the middle item is placed directly on the altar."
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"It is good to remember that the ritual will only happen if compatible spirits are on the altar, that is, requested in the recipe."
				""
				"It is possible to speed up the ritual using &9Runewood Obelisks&r"
			]
			icon: "malum:spirit_altar"
