			dependencies: ["0D6DAED46CCFA300"]
			description: [
				"The Coke Oven is a multiblock structure that  turns &5Coal&r into &5Coal Coke&r."
				""
				"&eHow to use&r: "
				"&e-&r Using a hopper or any type of piping items you insert coal. "
				"&e-&r While recipe is running, Coke Oven produces creosote and CO2."
				"&e-&r When recipe ends, the output is dropperd in the door of Coke Oven."
				""
				"Pressing &9W&r hovering &5Coke Oven&r you can see the ponder of structure."
				""
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"&a⚠ Tip:&r You can void CO2 Using Exhaust"
				""
				"&a⚠ Tip:&r Its recommended that you use more than one Coke Oven "
