		{
			dependencies: ["5884CEFF22577A10"]
			description: [
				"Your first way to obtain crude oil by-products is the Distillation Tower, it is a multi-block structure that receives oil through its controller and returns by-products through the outputs."
				""
				"&eHow to use&r:"
				"&e-&r Build structure like the ponder"
				"&e-&r Insert &5Crude Oil&r in &5Distillation Controller&r"
				"&e-&r Extract  by-products in &5Distillation Output&r"
				""
				"Pressing &9W&r hovering &5Steel Distillation Controller&r you can see the ponder of structure."
				""
				"{@pagebreak}"
				"&c⚠ Alert:&r  The structure pauses oil processing if the outputs are full, remember to pump the liquids to external tanks"
